{
  "texts": [
    "This global partitioning of the network into communities is called community detection.",
    "Many different community detection algorithms have been developed over the years and are reviewed in [17,25,26,74].Our community detection-based topic modeling algorithm Community Topic (CT) has three main steps.",
    "First, a network is constructed from the document corpus.",
    "After the network is constructed, CT applies a community detection algorithm to find the communities in the network.",
    "Finally, the communities are filtered out and, each topic (i.e., community) is sorted so that the most important and relevant terms for the topic come first and the topics are returned."
  ]
}